trans-unit.source: Indicates current system power status information.
The PowerStatus class represents information about the current AC line power status, battery charging status, and battery charge status.
trans-unit.target: Klassen PowerStatus representerer informasjon om gjeldende AC linje power status, lader batteristatus og batteristatus kostnader.

trans-unit.source: This class is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SystemInformation.PowerStatus%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SystemInformation> class to indicate current system power information.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen brukes av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SystemInformation.PowerStatus%2A>for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SystemInformation>klassen som viser informasjon om gjeldende power.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.SystemInformation> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.SystemInformation.PowerStatus%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets the current battery charge status.
This property indicates the current battery charge level or battery charging status.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen angir gjeldende kostnader nivå eller lading batteristatus.

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.BatteryChargeStatus"></xref> values indicating the current battery charge level or charging status.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.BatteryChargeStatus"> </xref> verdier som angir det gjeldende batteriet belaste nivået eller lading status.

trans-unit.source: Gets the reported full charge lifetime of the primary battery power source in seconds.
trans-unit.target: Henter rapporterte full kapasitet levetiden for primærbatteri power datakilden i sekunder.

trans-unit.source: The reported number of seconds of battery life available when the battery is fully charged, or -1 if the battery life is unknown.
trans-unit.target: Rapporterte antall sekunder for batterilevetid tilgjengelig når batteriet belastes fullstendig eller -1 Hvis batterilevetiden er ukjent.

trans-unit.source: Gets the approximate amount of full battery charge remaining.
trans-unit.target: Henter hvor Anslått gjenværende full batterikapasitet.

trans-unit.source: The approximate amount, from 0.0 to 1.0, of full battery charge remaining.
trans-unit.target: Hvor CA fra 0,0 1.0 i fullstendig batterikapasiteten gjenværende.

trans-unit.source: Gets the approximate number of seconds of battery time remaining.
trans-unit.target: Henter ca. antall sekunder uten batteri tid som gjenstår.

trans-unit.source: The approximate number of seconds of battery life remaining, or –1 if the approximate remaining battery life is unknown.
trans-unit.target: CA. antall sekunder for batteri liv gjenstående eller -1 Hvis Anslått gjenværende batterilevetiden er ukjent.

trans-unit.source: Gets the current system power status.
This property indicates whether the system power is online, or that the system power status is unknown.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen angir om datamaskinen er tilkoblet, eller at power systemstatus er ukjent.

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.PowerLineStatus"></xref> values indicating the current system power status.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.PowerLineStatus"> </xref> verdier som angir det gjeldende systemet power status.
